parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake booster can cause the brake pedal to become hard to press, leading to a loss of braking power, which can increase the risk of accidents and injuries.
symptoms: The brake pedal becomes hard to press
a hissing sound is heard when the brake pedal is pressed
the vehicle takes longer to stop
the brake pedal feels spongy
the vehicle's RPMs fluctuate when the brake pedal is pressed.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the water pump can cause the engine to overheat, leading to engine damage, stalling, or seizure, which can result in loss of power steering and brakes, increasing the risk of accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The check engine light comes on
the temperature gauge rises
the engine overheats
the vehicle stalls or loses power
the power steering and brakes fail
the vehicle makes loud noises
the coolant mixes with engine oil
and the engine oil becomes thick and sludgy.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Engine Failure Due to Water Pump Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the water pump can cause the engine to fail, resulting in costly repairs or replacement, and potentially leading to accidents or injuries due to loss of power steering and brakes.
symptoms: The engine fails
the vehicle stalls or loses power
the power steering and brakes fail
the engine makes loud noises
the coolant mixes with engine oil
and the engine oil becomes thick and sludgy.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering and brakes can increase the risk of accidents or injuries, especially at high speeds.
symptoms: The power steering and brakes fail
the vehicle is difficult to stop
the vehicle loses power
and the check engine light comes on.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Unintended airbag deployment can cause accidents, injuries, or fatalities due to sudden and unexpected loss of control, obstructed vision, or distraction.
symptoms: Sudden deployment of side curtain airbags
airbag warning lights
inability to see while driving
loss of control
and potential accidents.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure to properly recall and replace Takata airbags can lead to injuries or fatalities due to faulty airbag deployment.
symptoms: Confusion about recall status
lack of notification
and uncertainty about airbag safety.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Inconsistent or faulty passenger airbag deactivation can lead to inadequate protection in the event of an accident, increasing the risk of injury or fatality.
symptoms: Passenger airbag deactivation warning messages
inconsistent airbag activation
and uncertainty about airbag safety.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden failure of the water pump can cause catastrophic engine failure, leading to loss of engine power, inability to accelerate, and loss of control over steering and brakes, which can increase the risk of serious crashes.
symptoms: No warning or notice before failure
sudden loss of engine power
inability to accelerate
loss of control over steering and brakes
coolant leakage into the oil pan
and mixture of coolant and engine oil circulating through the engine.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The internal failure of the radiator can cause the mixture of antifreeze and engine oil, leading to engine destruction and potentially causing accidents.
symptoms: No warning or notice before failure
sudden loss of power
noise
and inability to start the engine
mixture of antifreeze and engine oil.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden shattering of the sunroof can cause injury to occupants and distraction to the driver, increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: Spontaneous shattering of the sunroof without any warning or external impact
showering glass inside the car.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure to properly repair recalled issues can lead to continued safety risks and frustration for vehicle owners.
symptoms: Lack of urgency in addressing recall repairs
failure to contact owners for repair appointments
and incomplete or ineffective repairs.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The faulty navigation system can cause inconvenience and distraction to the driver, potentially increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: Navigation system tracks faulty
inability to provide accurate directions
and repeated failure to repair the issue.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the front suspension can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents or injuries. It can also cause the wheel to detach from the vehicle, resulting in loss of steering and braking capabilities.
symptoms: Loud abnormal noise under the vehicle
front passenger tire twisted into the wheel well
vehicle stopped independently
wheel detached from the vehicle
difficulty steering and braking
hissing sound.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delayed repair of the front suspension recall can lead to accidents or injuries due to the failure of the suspension components.
symptoms: No symptoms reported
but the delay in repair can lead to the failure of the suspension components.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the sun visor can cause distraction while driving, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Sun visor no longer stays in place.
